Represents a document of any kind.
see [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-document](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-document)

Représente un document de n'importe quel type.

Documento Representa un documento de cualquier tipo.
ver [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-document](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-document)
